Summary: A modern and transparent way to use Windows VST2 and VST3 plugins on Linux
License: GPL-2.0-or-later
URL: https://github.com/robbert-vdh/yabridge
ExclusiveArch: x86_64 aarch64

Vendor:       Audinux
